high_descs: Head to the coffee machine on the left.
Pick up the mug on the coffee machine.
Bring the mug to the fridge on the right.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Bring the mug back to the coffee machine.
Put the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the coffee maker on the right
Grab the mug that is in the coffee maker
Turn right and head to the fridge
Open the fridge and place the mug on the top rack. Close the fridge. Open the fridge and grab the mug. Close the door.
Turn around and head to the coffee maker.
Place the mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Putting a mug in a coffee maker

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the coffee machine on the counter.
Pick up the white mug that is resting in the coffee machine.
Turn right and begin across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the mug inside and close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge, take the mug back out, then close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk around the kitchen island back over to where the coffee machine is on the counter.
Place the coffee mug back into the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled coffee mug in the coffee machine.
